{"tid":1567303,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中央政發委籲香港青年勿封閉在香港本土人環境　出路在內地","createTime":"2019-09-14T04:28:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T05:32:48.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"3b55fec2fff4a483229fbd9ee0f770224642511c","tid":1567303,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:28:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1480516_1_L_20190914105815.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1480516_1_L_20190914105815.jpg&h=8307d45f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中央政發委在微信公眾號發表文章，指內地為香港青年提供很多機遇，呼籲年輕人將眼界放遠，強調拿著激光筆，肯定畫不出五彩的人生。<br />\n<br />\n文章承認，年輕人面對就業難，工資低，房價高，但出路不在西方，而是自己的家，只要將眼界稍稍放遠，不要封閉在香港本土人的環境，不要困死在只說正宗粵語的小圈子，向北望去，內地可以提供更多就業、創業、創新及學習的機會。<br />\n<br />\n文章又說，不少年輕人喜歡標榜自己身在自由港，具有全球觀，習慣穿行在歐美日韓，將東南亞當作度假的後花園，但唯獨對全世界增速最快的經濟體、自己的祖國，視而不見，又引述有年輕人說不敢到內地，理由是怕在街上隨便被捉去坐監，認為視野之狹隘，觀點之滯後，令人扼腕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480516-20190914.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480516-20190914.htm&d=CilPfclB3esq2vqCdqPDZxURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=e32beda5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480516-20190914.htm&h=17bc2078\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480516-20190914.htm</a>"},{"pid":"967aa434c15b0fed9fc4d890957c3ad7ac47b08b","tid":1567303,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:29:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f0e50e7dabc37f0166d48c219e2440e3d648206","tid":1567303,"uid":152476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:29:17.000Z","msg":"井底蛙話唔入井底既人自我封閉<br />\n香港人要走出國際囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8136a184eb597d20f5b1ce7c9